author=";s:7:"metakey";s:0:"";s:7:"plugins";s:0:"";s:8:"language";s:1:"*";s:12:"categoryname";s:21:"Стиль жизни";s:10:"categoryid";s:2:"14";s:13:"categoryalias";s:11:"stil-zhizni";s:14:"categoryparams";s:2849:"{"theme":"default","num_leading_items":"2","num_leading_columns":"1","leadingImgSize":"Large","num_primary_items":"4","num_primary_columns":"2","primaryImgSize":"Medium","num_secondary_items":"4","num_secondary_columns":"1","secondaryImgSize":"Small","num_links":"4","num_links_columns":"1","linksImgSize":"XSmall","catCatalogMode":"0","catFeaturedItems":"1","catOrdering":"","catPagination":"2","catPaginationResults":"1","catTitle":"1","catTitleItemCounter":"1","catDescription":"1","catImage":"1","catFeedLink":"1","catFeedIcon":"1","subCategories":"1","subCatColumns":"2","subCatOrdering":"","subCatTitle":"1","subCatTitleItemCounter":"1","subCatDescription":"1","subCatImage":"1","itemImageXS":"","itemImageS":"","itemImageM":"","itemImageL":"","itemImageXL":"","catItemTitle":"1","catItemTitleLinked":"1","catItemFeaturedNotice":"0","catItemAuthor":"1","catItemDateCreated":"1","catItemRating":"0","catItemImage":"1","catItemIntroText":"1","catItemIntroTextWordLimit":"","catItemExtraFields":"0","catItemHits":"0","catItemCategory":"1","catItemTags":"1","catItemAttachments":"0","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"0","catItemVideo":"0","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"0","catItemImageGallery":"0","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"0","catItemReadMore":"1","catItemCommentsAnchor":"1","catItemK2Plugins":"1","itemDateCreated":"1","itemTitle":"1","itemFeaturedNotice":"1","itemAuthor":"1","itemFontResizer":"1","itemPrintButton":"1","itemEmailButton":"1","itemSocialButton":"1","itemVideoAnchor":"1","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"1","itemCommentsAnchor":"1","itemRating":"1","itemImage":"1","itemImgSize":"Large","itemImageMainCaption":"1","itemImageMainCredits":"1","itemIntroText":"1","itemFullText":"1","itemExtraFields":"1","itemDateModified":"1","itemHits":"1","itemCategory":"1","itemTags":"1","itemAttachments":"1","itemAttachmentsCounter":"1","itemVideo":"1","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"0","itemVideoCaption":"1","itemVideoCredits":"1","itemImageGallery":"1","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"1","itemComments":"1","itemTwitterButton":"1","itemFacebookButton":"1","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"1","itemAuthorBlock":"1","itemAuthorImage":"1","itemAuthorDescription":"1","itemAuthorURL":"1","itemAuthorEmail":"0","itemAuthorLatest":"1","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"5","itemRelated":"1","itemRelatedLimit":"5","itemRelatedTitle":"1","itemRelatedCategory":"0","itemRelatedImageSize":"0","itemRelatedIntrotext":"0","itemRelatedFulltext":"0","itemRelatedAuthor":"0","itemRelatedMedia":"0","itemRelatedImageGallery":"0","itemK2Plugins":"1","catMetaDesc":"","catMetaKey":"","catMetaRobots":"","catMetaAuthor":""}";s:9:"itemGroup";s:7:"leading";s:8:"category";O:15:"TableK2Category":27:{s:2:"id";s:2:"14";s:4:"name";s:21:"Стиль жизни";s:5:"alias";s:11:"stil-zhizni";s:11:"description";s:2427:"<p class="pdng">Некоторые читатели даже зададут вопрос по другому: "Что же это такое стиль жизни? Непонятно..." Да, не все это понимают. Задавая себе этот вопрос, вспомните Диогена. Отрицая материальные ценности, обитал в бочке, проповедуя свои истины. Такой вот стиль жизни был у человека.</p>
<p class="pdng">По моему мнению, понятие стиля жизни актуально тем людям, движущей силой которых является предпочтение, а не потребности. По&nbsp;<a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BC%D0%B8%D0%B4%D0%B0_%D0%BF%D0%BE%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B1%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%B9_%D0%BF%D0%BE_%D0%9C%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%83" target="_blank">пирамиде потребности Маслоу</a>&nbsp;это характеристика более зрелой личности. Вы,конечно же&nbsp;поняли, я о предпочтении. Короче говоря, стиль жизни это то, что вы есть.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="pdng">На стиль жизни влияют очень разные факторы и условия. Как правило, все те же, что влияют на формирование личности. Ну а если его (стиля) нет - нет и личности.</p>
<p class="pdng">Словами создателя собственной психоаналитической концепции&nbsp;<a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%90%D0%B4%D0%BB%D0%B5%D1%80,_%D0%90%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%84%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B4" target="_blank">Альфреда Адлера</a>&nbsp;"Стиль жизни включает в себя уникальные соединения черт, способов поведения и привычек, которые все вместе определяют неповторимую картину существования человека". От стиля жизни зависят его основные &nbsp;приоритеты а также показатели его успешной деятельности и состоятельности.</p>";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:16:"extraFieldsGroup";s:1:"0";s:9:"published";s:1:"1";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:6:"access";s:1:"1";s:8:"ordering";s:1:"6";s:6:"params";s:2849:"{"theme":"default","num_leading_items":"2","num_leading_columns":"1","leadingImgSize":"Large","num_primary_items":"4","num_primary_columns":"2","primaryImgSize":"Medium","num_secondary_items":"4","num_secondary_columns":"1","secondaryImgSize":"Small","num_links":"4","num_links_columns":"1","linksImgSize":"XSmall","catCatalogMode":"0","catFeaturedItems":"1","catOrdering":"","catPagination":"2","catPaginationResults":"1","catTitle":"1","catTitleItemCounter":"1","catDescription":"1","catImage":"1","catFeedLink":"1","catFeedIcon":"1","subCategories":"1","subCatColumns":"2","subCatOrdering":"","subCatTitle":"1","subCatTitleItemCounter":"1","subCatDescription":"1","subCatImage":"1","itemImageXS":"","itemImageS":"","itemImageM":"","itemImageL":"","itemImageXL":"","catItemTitle":"1","catItemTitleLinked":"1","catItemFeaturedNotice":"0","catItemAuthor":"1","catItemDateCreated":"1","catItemRating":"0","catItemImage":"1","catItemIntroText":"1","catItemIntroTextWordLimit":"","catItemExtraFields":"0","catItemHits":"0","catItemCategory":"1","catItemTags":"1","catItemAttachments":"0","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"0","catItemVideo":"0","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"0","catItemImageGallery":"0","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","cat